Name: Eeekeemoo: Splinters of the Dark Shard

Achievements.Description: Try bouncing on a Jump Pod...25 times should do it.

Achievements.Name: Release Woodface
Achievements.Description: Help release Woodface from his eternal torment.

Achievements.Name: Release Hammerfist
Achievements.Description: Poor Guy...just wanted to continue his work. Release him

Achievements.Description: Defeat Harry, he cannot be saved...release him from his pain.

Achievements.Name: Avoid Li Pha
Achievements.Description: Avoid Li Pha, at all costs

Achievements.Name: Escape The Lava Lakes
Achievements.Description: Don't get burnt on your way out.

Achievements.Name: Escape The Frozen Fortress
Achievements.Description: Chilling experience, watch you don't get frozen on the spot.

Achievements.Name: Escape the Dark Cave
Achievements.Description: Wonder through the cave until you get lost, repeat until you get out...good luck!
